Other Datasets

Source: vignettes/dolrother.Rmd
dolrother.Rmd

Examples

The code chunks below shows how to query the other datasets available. For official documentation go to: https://developer.dol.gov/others/

Agency 

library(dolr)
library(stringr)
library(knitr)

# Set the key
dolsetkey("3e28950b-f0f0-4ba1-b7ec-e4ce5c112779")

kable(head(str_trunc(dol_oth(dataset = 10, sheet = 1), 10, ellipsis = "...")))
__metadata Agency AgencyFullName WebsiteURL MissionURL OrganizationalURL KeyPersonnelURL
https:/… ARB… Adminis… http://… http://… http://… http://…
https:/… BLS… Bureau … http://… http://… http://… http://…
https:/… BRB… Benefit… http://… http://… http://… http://…
https:/… CFBNP… Center … http://… http://… NULL… http://…
https:/… EBSA… Employe… http://… http://… http://… http://…
https:/… ECAB… Employe… http://… http://… http://… http://…

# x <- dol_oth(dataset = 10, sheet = 1)

Research And Evaluation Inventory 


# This queries the Research and Evaluation Inventory consisting of various documents.
# There is only one sheet associated with this dataset: researchEvaluationInventory
kable(head(str_trunc(dol_oth(dataset = 5, sheet = 1), 10, ellipsis = "..."))[1:7])
__metadata id dolAgency description status beginDate datePublished

Geography
